ERROR #3 - Login Mutation Returns Null
================================================================================

Observed behavior:
- GraphQL mutation login returned:
  { "data": { "login": null } }

Root cause:
- A stale Node server process was running on port 4000
- npm start failed with EADDRINUSE, so old process continued serving requests
- Requests hit that old instance, which didn't have the latest code

Solution:
1. Killed stale process on port 4000 (pid 2801, 8646, etc.)
2. Restarted server with npm start
3. Retried mutation

Result after fix:
- login returned valid token, username, and userId

